465
00:46:42,548 --> 00:46:43,717
Soa divertido, não?

466
00:46:44,617 --> 00:46:45,686
De modo que...

467
00:46:46,452 --> 00:46:47,487
Quem és?

468
00:46:49,389 --> 00:46:50,389
Sou Prince.

469
00:46:51,523 --> 00:46:53,726
